"Abstract What about this for a dramatic opener? “Greetings! Without your knowledge or explicit permission, the Windows networking technology which connects your computer to the Internet may be offering some or all of your computer’s data to the entire world at this very moment!” The website from which this is taken is called Shields Up ( https://grc.com ) and is dedicated to researching Internet security for Windows users. There are tools here for the taking that will give you an instant picture of your current level of security — or lack of it, as the case may be."
